snippet.title: Port Royale 3 Announcement Trailer (US)
snippet.description: This is the announcement trailer for Port Royale 3, the upcoming historic caribbean economic simulation by Gaming Minds Studio and Kalypso Media. Find out more at www.kalypsomedia.com !
